hiya befallen is not the place to be if you are alone at lvl 15, this i can
tell ya from personal exp. the keys are to the doors of lvl 1,2,&3, the one
that dissapeared will always dissapear un lerr you put the key in a bag and
in the bank. so thats what i do i have a complete set of befallen keys in a
bag in my bank account, you can get barbed sleeves there but i forgot off
which npc, nice stats on them too. there is a malot head and a shaft for it
somewhere, i beleive this is a quest but it also has nice stats. anywya
thats all i know im sure someone else can tell ya more *hugs*
